        <h2>Common Baking Errors</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Problem:</strong> Cake is too dense.<br>
                <strong>Solution:</strong> Ensure your leavening agents (baking soda/powder) are fresh and accurately measured.</li>
            <li><strong>Problem:</strong> Cookies spread too much.<br>
                <strong>Solution:</strong> Chill the dough before baking and use the correct flour type.</li>
            <li><strong>Problem:</strong> Muffins are dry.<br>
                <strong>Solution:</strong> Donâ€™t overmix the batter and check your oven temperature.</li>
